                </p>
            </marquee>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="slider-game">
    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="owl-carousel owl-theme owl-loaded">
            <div class="owl-stage-outer">
                <div class="owl-stage">
                    <div class="owl-item">
                        <div class="card">
                            <img class="card-img-top img-fluid" src="~/images/slider-game/NEW-HP_26.jpg" />
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Buy</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="owl-item">
                        <div class="card">
                            <img class="card-img-top img-fluid" src="~/images/slider-game/NEW-HP_26.jpg" />
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Buy</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="owl-item">
                        <div class="card">
                            <img class="card-img-top img-fluid" src="~/images/slider-game/NEW-HP_26.jpg" />
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Buy</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="owl-item">
                        <div class="card">
                            <img class="card-img-top img-fluid" src="~/images/slider-game/NEW-HP_26.jpg" />
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Buy</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="app-content container center-layout mt-2">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="content-header row">
            <div class="content-header-left col-md-6 col-12 mb-2 breadcrumb-new">

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content-body">
            <section id="description" class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h4 class="card-title">Description</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="card-text">
                            <p>Vertical collapsible navigation menu open or close only on menu click, it is useful for those menu have less menu item and need remain open last clicked menu option. You can experience collapsible navigation in left side menu.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@section scripts{
    <script src="~/js/dashboard/plugins/owl-carousel/owl.carousel.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/dashboard/marquee.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/dashboard/cpl.home.js"></script>
}